  "document": "=============================================\n\nAuthor: Ascendion AAVA\n\nCreated on:\n\nDescription: Bronze layer ETL pipeline orchestrator loading 12 target tables with audit logging\n\n=============================================\n\n# 1. Overview of Program\n\nThis stored procedure orchestrates the bronze layer ETL pipeline by sequentially invoking 12 individual table load procedures, each responsible for loading data from source layer to bronze layer tables. The procedure implements comprehensive audit logging, batch tracking, and error handling to ensure data lineage and execution monitoring across all table loads.\n\n# 2. Code Structure and Design\n\n- Declares procedure bronze.usp_Load_bronze_Layer_Full with no input parameters\n- Declares 16 variables for procedure name, timestamps, execution metrics, error details, batch tracking, and current user\n- Generates batch ID from start timestamp formatted as 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS.FF3'\n- Logs pipeline start information including start time, executing user, and batch ID using DBMS_OUTPUT\n- Invokes bronze.usp_Load_bz_New_Monthly_HC_Report for multiple tables: bz_New_Monthly_HC_Report, bz_SchTask, bz_Hiring_Initiator_Project_Info, bz_Timesheet_New, bz_report_392_all, bz_vw_billing_timesheet_daywise_ne, bz_vw_consultant_timesheet_daywise, bz_DimDate, bz_holidays_Mexico, bz_holidays_Canada, bz_holidays, bz_holidays_India\n- Increments v_TablesProcessed counter after each procedure invocation\n- Queries bronze.bz_Audit_Log table to calculate summary statistics for successful loads\n- Queries bronze.bz_Audit_Log table to calculate summary statistics for failed loads\n- Calculates total rows processed by summing inserted and failed rows\n- Calculates execution time by extracting day, hour, minute, and second components from timestamp difference\n- Logs completion summary including end time, execution time, tables processed, success/failure counts, and row counts using DBMS_OUTPUT\n- Inserts master audit record into bronze.bz_Audit_Log with aggregated metrics and load type 'FULL_REFRESH_ALL_TABLES'\n- Commits transaction after successful completion\n- Implements exception handler to capture error details including SQLERRM and SQLCODE\n- Logs error information including error number, severity, state, line, and message using DBMS_OUTPUT in exception block\n- Inserts error audit record into bronze.bz_Audit_Log with error details and status 'FAILED' in exception block\n- Commits transaction in exception block\n- Raises application error with error code -20001 and captured error message\n\n# 3. Data Flow and Processing Logic\n\n```text\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n| START            | -> | INITIALIZE VARS  | -> | GENERATE BATCH   | -> | LOG START        |\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n                                                                                          |\n                                                                                          v\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n| LOAD TABLE 4     | <- | LOAD TABLE 3     | <- | LOAD TABLE 2     | <- | LOAD TABLE 1     |\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n         |                                                                                 \n         v                                                                                 \n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n| LOAD TABLE 5     | -> | LOAD TABLE 6     | -> | LOAD TABLE 7     | -> | LOAD TABLE 8     |\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n                                                                                          |\n                                                                                          v\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n| LOAD TABLE 12    | <- | LOAD TABLE 11    | <- | LOAD TABLE 10    | <- | LOAD TABLE 9     |\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n         |                                                                                 \n         v                                                                                 \n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n| QUERY SUCCESS    | -> | QUERY FAILURES   | -> | CALC TOTALS      | -> | CALC EXEC TIME   |\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n                                                                                          |\n                                                                                          v\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n| END              | <- | COMMIT           | <- | INSERT AUDIT     | <- | LOG COMPLETION   |\n+------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+    +------------------+\n                                                                                          |\n                                                                                          v\n                                               +------------------+    +------------------+\n                                               | LOG ERROR        | <- | ERROR HANDLER    |\n                                               +------------------+    +------------------+\n                                                         |                                 \n                                                         v                                 \n                                               +------------------+    +------------------+\n                                               | RAISE ERROR      | <- | COMMIT           |\n                                               +------------------+    +------------------+\n                                                                              |\n                                                                              v\n                                                                    +------------------+\n                                                                    | INSERT ERROR LOG |\n                                                                    +------------------+\n```\n\n# 4. Data Mapping\n\n| Target Object Name | Target Attribute Name | Source Object Name | Source Attribute Name | Remarks |\n|--------------------|-----------------------|--------------------|-----------------------|---------|\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | source_table | Literal | 'source_layer.*' | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | target_table | Literal | 'bronze.*' | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | load_timestamp | Variable | v_StartTime | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | start_timestamp | Variable | v_StartTime | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | end_timestamp | Variable | v_EndTime | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | processed_by | Variable | v_CurrentUser | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | processing_time | Variable | v_ExecutionTime | Derived attribute |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | status | Variable | v_OverallStatus | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | records_processed | Variable | v_TotalRowsProcessed | Derived attribute |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | records_inserted | Variable | v_TotalRowsInserted | Aggregation rule |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | records_failed | Variable | v_TotalRowsFailed | Aggregation rule |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | batch_id | Variable | v_BatchID | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | load_type | Literal | 'FULL_REFRESH_ALL_TABLES' | 1 to 1 mapping |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | created_date | Function | SYSTIMESTAMP | Function rule |\n| bronze.bz_Audit_Log | error_message | Variable | v_ErrorMessage | Conditional logic |\n\n# 5. Complexity Analysis\n\n| Category | Measurement |\n|----------|-------------|\n| Number of Transformations | 0 |\n| Number of ETL Processes | 12 |\n| Number of Target Tables / Objects | 13 |\n| Number of Source Tables / Objects | 1 |\n| Number of Data Loads | 12 |\n| Number of JOIN Operations | 0 |\n| Number of Aggregation Operations | 4 |\n| Number of Sorting Operations | 0 |\n| Number of Cursors | 0 |\n| Number of Loops | 0 |\n| Conditional Logic Blocks | 0 |\n| Error Handling Blocks | 1 |\n| Logging/Audit Mechanisms | 3 |\n| External Dependencies | 12 |\n| System Integrations | 0 |\n| Overall Complexity Score (0–100) | 45 |\n\n# 6. Sensitive and Privacy Data Assessment\n\nNo sensitive data found\n\n# 7. Key Outputs\n\n- Inserts master audit record into bronze.bz_Audit_Log table with aggregated pipeline execution metrics\n- Loads 12 bronze layer tables: bz_New_Monthly_HC_Report, bz_SchTask, bz_Hiring_Initiator_Project_Info, bz_Timesheet_New, bz_report_392_all, bz_vw_billing_timesheet_daywise_ne, bz_vw_consultant_timesheet_daywise, bz_DimDate, bz_holidays_Mexico, bz_holidays_Canada, bz_holidays, bz_holidays_India\n- Generates batch ID for tracking and lineage across all table loads\n\n# 8. API Cost Calculations\n\nAPI cost for this call: 0.0000 USD"
